verse = \lyricmode {
  Had we the name of God neg -- lect -- ed,
had we to for -- eign gods de -- fect -- ed,
you would have seen it long a -- go.
All se -- crets of the heart you know.
Yet for your sake we all day long
face death like sheep soon to be slaugh -- tered.
Our e -- ne -- mies are fierce and strong;
we have been o -- ver -- whelmed and scat -- tered.
}
